    text: "\n\nEdit documents refers to the process of making changes to a document in order to improve its accuracy, clarity, and/or formatting. This can include correcting spelling and grammar mistakes, adding or removing content, and rearranging the document's structure. Editing documents is an important part of the writing process, as it ensures that the final product is of the highest quality.",
