    text: "\n\nis a business process problem/issue that involves identifying the root cause of a problem and developing a solution to address it. This could involve analyzing the current process, identifying areas of improvement, and developing a plan to implement the changes. It could also involve gathering feedback from stakeholders, testing the proposed solution, and monitoring the results. Ultimately, the goal is to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of the business process.",
