    indicator:
      "Describe requirements for aligning information technology and business strategy to leverage dataas a strategic asset (SM:079) ",
    text: "\n\nAligning information technology and business strategy to leverage data as a strategic asset requires a comprehensive approach. This includes understanding the business objectives, developing a data strategy that aligns with those objectives, and then implementing the necessary technology to support the data strategy. Additionally, organizations must ensure that the data is secure, accurate, and accessible to the right people at the right time. Finally, organizations must have a plan for how to use the data to inform decision-making, measure performance, and create competitive advantage.",
