    indicator: "Explain the concept of product mix (PM:003) ",
    text: "\n\nProduct mix is the combination of products and services that a company offers to its customers. It is an important part of a company's overall marketing strategy and can include a variety of products and services that are tailored to meet the needs of different customer segments. Product mix can include items such as physical products, services, digital products, and even intangible products such as warranties and guarantees. The product mix can also be used to differentiate a company from its competitors by offering unique products and services that are not available elsewhere.",
