    indicator:
      "Monitor and mine sales data (by volume, product, territory, channel, time period, etc.) (IM:379)",
    text: "\n\nMonitoring and mining sales data involves collecting and analyzing data related to sales volume, product, territory, channel, and time period. This data can be used to identify trends, identify opportunities for improvement, and make informed decisions about sales strategies. By monitoring and mining sales data, businesses can gain insights into customer behavior, identify areas of growth, and optimize their sales strategies.",
