    text: "\n\nBanking security tools and technology are essential for protecting customers' financial information and assets. Remote drive-up equipment, such as ATMs, allow customers to access their accounts without having to enter a physical bank. Safe deposit boxes and vaults provide secure storage for important documents and valuables. Alarm systems alert bank personnel of any suspicious activity. All of these tools and technologies help to ensure the safety and security of customers' financial information and assets.",
    category: ["FINANCE"],
