    text: "\n\nFollowing trends in the popularity of destinations and packages means keeping up with the latest information about the most popular places to visit and the most sought-after vacation packages. This could include researching the most popular tourist attractions, researching the most popular vacation packages, and staying up to date on the latest news and trends in the travel industry. By staying informed, you can ensure that you are offering the best possible options for your customers.",
